<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٥:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَيَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ الْجِبَالِ فَقُلْ يَنْسِفُهَا رَبِّي نَسْفًا <span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span> فَيَذَرُهَا قَاعًا صَفْصَفًا <span class="c2">(١٠٦)</span> لَا تَرَى فِيهَا عِوَجًا وَلَا أَمْتًا <span class="c2">(١٠٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[طه: ١٠٥ - ١٠٧]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{قَاعًا}</span>: يَعْلُوهُ المَاءُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَالصَّفْصَفُ:</span> المُسْتَوِي مِنَ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{عِوَجًا}</span>: <span class="c2">«وَادِيًا»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَلاَ أَمْتًا}</span>: <span class="c2">«رَابِيَةً»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>